BT /F1 15 Tf 0.051 0.078 0.094 rg 58 760 Td (4. What the system returns) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 0.051 0.078 0.094 rg 58 728 Td (Every meaningful action should return a receipt.) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 0.051 0.078 0.094 rg 58 705 Td (A receipt is not bureaucracy. It is proof that the task was received, handled, or) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 0.051 0.078 0.094 rg 58 690 Td (escalated. It should make the status visible without forcing someone to hunt) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 0.051 0.078 0.094 rg 58 675 Td (through chats, docs, inboxes, and dashboards.) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 0.051 0.078 0.094 rg 58 652 Td (If nobody can see where the work is, the system is not finished.) Tj ET
BT /F1 15 Tf 0.051 0.078 0.094 rg 58 629 Td (5. Where AI actually earns its keep) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 0.051 0.078 0.094 rg 58 597 Td (AI is useful where judgment, synthesis, language, prioritization, or pattern) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 0.051 0.078 0.094 rg 58 582 Td (recognition changes the outcome.) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 0.051 0.078 0.094 rg 58 559 Td (It is much less useful as a substitute for basic plumbing. If the task is already) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 0.051 0.078 0.094 rg 58 544 Td (clear and repeatable, the better answer may be a rule, form, queue, or) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 0.051 0.078 0.094 rg 58 529 Td (notification.) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 0.051 0.078 0.094 rg 58 506 Td (The commercial win is not "more AI." It is fewer dropped handoffs, less manual) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 0.051 0.078 0.094 rg 58 491 Td (transfer, and more time spent on decisions that actually matter.) Tj ET
BT /F1 15 Tf 0.051 0.078 0.094 rg 58 468 Td (6. A practical first step) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 0.051 0.078 0.094 rg 58 436 Td (Pick one recurring handoff that wastes time.) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 0.051 0.078 0.094 rg 58 413 Td (Use four questions:) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 0.051 0.078 0.094 rg 58 390 Td (- Where is the work captured?) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 0.051 0.078 0.094 rg 58 367 Td (- Who or what decides where it goes?) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 0.051 0.078 0.094 rg 58 344 Td (- What action is expected next?) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 0.051 0.078 0.094 rg 58 321 Td (- What receipt proves it happened?) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 0.051 0.078 0.094 rg 58 298 Td (If any answer depends on someone remembering, searching, or copying from one tool) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 0.051 0.078 0.094 rg 58 283 Td (to another, that is the first place to fix.) Tj ET
BT /F1 15 Tf 0.051 0.078 0.094 rg 58 260 Td (7. CTA) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 0.051 0.078 0.094 rg 58 228 Td (Comment or DM "SYSTEM" if you want a practical way to find the handoffs wasting) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 0.051 0.078 0.094 rg 58 213 Td (time in your business.) Tj ET
BT /F2 8 Tf 0.318 0.376 0.408 rg 58 32 Td (Time to Revenue) Tj ET
endstream
